text: <@U02LU2TBX44> Seem you try to fetch the API data with your browser, that's client side and the request is forbidden by the browser security policies. That is mean by CORS. Create your own Endpoint on your external Server and fetch the HubSpot- API data server side. Next, provide a router for your requests, where you can set the required 'Access-Control-Allow-Origin' header and return the data.
